ober 12, 2013 on the terms included in the CSC/Pamplona final proposal and authorized the Transaction Committee and Goodwin Procter to continue negotiations with CSC/Pamplona based on guidance provided by the Special Committee at this meeting.', 'is_heading': False, 'page_break_before': False, 'page_break_after': False, 'date_mentions': [{'raw_text': 'September 23, 2013', 'normalized': '2013-09-23', 'precision': 'exact_day'}, {'raw_text': 'October 12, 2013', 'normalized': '2013-10-12', 'precision': 'exact_day'}], 'entity_mentions': [{'raw_text': 'Special Committee', 'entity_type': 'committee'}, {'raw_text': 'Transaction Committee', 'entity_type': 'committee'}], 'evidence_density': 5, 'temporal_phase': 'outcome'}
